{"tid":286890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我曾經偷渡去台灣 坐咗一年 你問我唔答","createTime":"2017-06-17T03:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T13:59:22.000Z","uid":16383,"like":203,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a5381276ec33379ec329c207ee50cc63b0dccdd2","tid":286890,"uid":16383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:52:14.000Z","msg":"用「持用假文件非法入境」入罪 判一年有期徒刑<br />\n曾經我俾人叫我 <span style=\"color: gold;\">馬仔</span><br />\n因為我以前做貨運嘅<br />\n所以我運<span style=\"font-size: large;\">貨</span> 成日都要跑<br />\n啲 就叫我馬仔喇<br />\n一個唔好彩 跑得慢得濟 搞到要坐大飛<br />\n但係都要俾人拉 坐咗一年 一年話長唔長 話短唔短<br />\n我係入面諗 如果Oriental spider可以有少少變化<br />\n可以令我故鄉-香港 有啲變化可以點呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩想問 我驚自爆 未必會答"},{"pid":"71dd968fc5731738b0f6b14fc854cadf5ef4f2cd","tid":286890,"uid":16383,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"講多少少 我係賣白飯同運蝦片起家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e6299dabe859a2cabf84458e9d552c4efc2941","tid":286890,"uid":43707,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"點解做運貨？"},{"pid":"93c859525b8d6f5f0fffbf4d3bf9b098d9bc5e80","tid":286890,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解做運貨？</blockquote><br />\n都幾好搵㗎 嗰陣同呀哥拍住上"},{"pid":"b260ea9bd12f0ebba32c2e0cead2dba26e721867","tid":286890,"uid":43707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解做運貨？</blockquote><br />\n都幾好搵㗎 嗰陣同呀哥拍住上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未坐之前唔驚比人拉？"},{"pid":"93d943649972366bda3613c189130531943d0b1a","tid":286890,"uid":19542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"雖難必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee1eadd1653ead0f03c6520d0e4a299c023c075","tid":286890,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor